non-func

The system shall protect the data of every driver
The system shall implement a user-friendly UI
The system shall provide up to date information on services
The system shall be robust against user input



func

The system must allow a driver to make a holiday
The system must allow a users to look up various timetables
The system must allow a driver a roster to be generated
The system must allow a driver to report an illness
The system must allow passengers to view any service changes
The system must display route and service information
The system must find a replacement driver when drivers are ill/on holiday
The system must find a substitute bus and driver when buses break down
The system must provide sufficient buses at all times


